Class Asn1DateTime

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Asn1TypeIF, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable

    public class Asn1DateTime
extends Asn18BitCharString
    This is a container class for holding the components of an ASN.1 DATE-TIME value.
    See Also:
    Serialized Form

        public void encode(Asn1PerOutputStream out)

        This method encodes an ASN.1 DATE-TIME value in accordance with the packed encoding rules (PER) directly into the stream.
